window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Abysses End has left for the time being, but they left behind a parting gift of sorts. Meanwhile in Eternal Dominion the major workshops are stirring up trouble for FAE to waylay their progress. All while Alex/Xeal tries to advance himself and his guild further in both reality and the virtual world once more.</p> <p>Will FAE succeed in fending off the latest moves from the major players, and what other surprises does life have instore for Alex/Xeal.</p>"; 
